	h1={`The Bible for the Incarcerated`}
	heroEyebrow={`A Father For`}
	heroSubhead={`A cell can hold your body, a label can follow your name, and the world can decide it's done with you — but none of that gets the last word. You have a Father in heaven whose love reaches through any wall, who has not forgotten you, and who can set your heart free long before the doors ever open.`}
